timelineItems.text: #GoCity RT" 75' FC Dallas substitution: Rolando Escobar on for Michael Barrios. #ORLvDAL 0-2 http://t.co/vAOIb7hOSn "#SportsRoadhouse

timelineItems.desc: Dan Kennedy (FC Dallas) is shown the yellow card for a bad foul.
timelineItems.title: PENALTY: The referee points to the spot after Dan Kennedy brings down Pedro Ribeiro

timelineItems.desc: Penalty missed! Bad penalty by Carlos Rivas (Orlando City SC) left footed shot is close, but misses the top left corner.
timelineItems.title: PK MISS: Carlos Rivas skies the penalty Pedro Ribeiro earned

timelineItems.name: The Mane Land
timelineItems.text: 88' PENALTY ORLANDO CITY. Dan Kennedy absolutely CRUSHES Pedro Ribeiro. How is that not a red card?! #ORLvDAL

timelineItems.name: Christian Bruey
timelineItems.text: Kennedy with an obvious penalty. Destroyed @pedronalribeiro. Not sure how that isn't a red! #ORLvDAL

timelineItems.name: Ian
timelineItems.text: THAT SHOULD BE RED!!!!! #ORLvDAL

timelineItems.name: Gavin Ewbank
timelineItems.text: Five minutes to go, down by two goals, plenty of fans have already begun filing out of the Citrus Bowl. #ORLvDAL

timelineItems.name: ESPN 580
timelineItems.text: Rivas does what only Rivas can do and he sends the PK into row 23 behind the goal #ORLvDAL

timelineItems.name: Orlando Soccer Daily
timelineItems.text: 89' Ouch. Rivas belts the PK way above the bar. It's been one of those nights. #ORLvDAL

timelineItems.desc: Second yellow card to Luke Boden (Orlando City SC) for a bad foul.
timelineItems.title: RED CARD: Luke Boden gets his second yellow and a sending off for a wayward elbow

timelineItems.name: Orlando Soccer Daily
timelineItems.text: For perhaps the first time this season fans are starting to leave early. #ORLvDAL

timelineItems.name: Christian Bruey
timelineItems.text: That should quiet all those fans who want @Kaka taken off the PK duties for @OrlandoCitySC. #ORLvDAL

timelineItems.name: Orlando City SC
timelineItems.text: 89' MISS. Rivas launches the PK high and left. Not much time left for Orlando now. http://t.co/0DvNhLbbD7 #ORLvDAL 0-2

timelineItems.name: The Mane Land
timelineItems.text: Somehow, only 2 minutes of stoppage time. Unbelievable. #ORLvDAL

timelineItems.name: Matt Young
timelineItems.text: Well, when it rains, it pours. Nothing has gone right for City tonight #OCSC #ORLvDAL

timelineItems.name: Matthew Kirby
timelineItems.text: Boden now sent off for Orlando. From bad to worse! Won't have a team next week! #ORLvDAL
